title: Pennsylvania attorney general charged with 2nd perjury count
text: > Pennsylvania Pennsylvania attorney general charged with 2nd perjury count FILE - In this Aug. 12, 2015 file photo Pennsylvania Attorney General Kathleen Kane speaks during a news conference at the state Capitol in Harrisburg, Pa. Kane faces a new charge Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015 that stems from evidence found during an execution of a search warrant at her office Sept. 17. Kane was previously charged with perjury, conspiracy and other counts. Prosecutors say she leaked confidential information from a 2009 grand jury probe and then tried to cover it up. (AP Photo/Matt Rourke, File)
